= GUI infrastructure =

Desktop Experience:

= Desktop apps =

We use many GNOME applications as part of our desktop user interface. Rather than using Debian's meta-packages they are deliberately expanded so that we can select things a bit better.

 * baobab
 * cheese
 * gnome-characters
 * goldendict
 * gucharmap
 * gtkhash
 * hardinfo
 * hexchat
 * libreoffice
 * lm-sensors
 * simple-pwgen
 * syncthing
 * variety
 * vlc-plugin-access-extra

= Other =

 * mamolinux-desktop-full # metapackage for everything here
